  "content": "<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>33. Have you been removed from any legal agreements or property titles?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>SECTION 8: DIGITAL &amp DEVICE ACCESS</tt></b></div>\n<div><b><tt>34. Did someone access the deceased’s phone, email, or computer?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>35. Any suspicious logins or password changes post-death?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>36. Has anyone impersonated the deceased digitally or otherwise?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><tt><br></tt></div>\n<div><b><tt>SECTION 9: LEGAL / MEDICAL FORGERY</tt></b></div>\n<div><b><tt>37. Any pressure on the deceased to sign documents in final weeks?</tt></b><tt><br></tt></div>",
